name: Cartel
description: I used the ape as a symbol from ancient times to modern times like now.As far as I understand a "cartel" is a group of independent market producers who cooperate with each other to increase profits and dominate the market. Cartels are usually associations in the same business field, and are alliances of competitors. From this explanation I see that the "Crypto" market is very popular now where there is fierce competition in the meta world.
